[3-Kingdom] Stat-Arb v3.0 Project Ignore List

Trading Data & Sensitive Information (CRITICAL)

Ignore API keys and private connection configs

config/config.yaml
.env

Ignore all generated trade data, signals and logs

data/
result/
*.csv
*.parquet
*.json

2. Python Environment & Cache

Ignore compiled python files

pycache/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so

Ignore local virtual environments

venv/
.venv/
env/
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

3. IDE & System Metadata

JetBrains (PyCharm)

.idea/

VS Code

.vscode/
.history/

Operating System Files

.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

4. Specific Exclusions (Optional)

If you want to keep the folder structure but ignore content,

uncomment below:

!data/.gitkeep

!result/.gitkeep